config BR2_PACKAGE_AIC8800
    bool "aic8800"
    depends on BR2_LINUX_KERNEL
    depends on BR2_USE_MMU
    help
      Aicsemi AIC8800 / AIC8800DC / AIC8800DW / AIC8800FC USB Wi-Fi
      driver (Radxa fork). Provides Wi-Fi 6 support on the Luckfox
      Pico Zero target. Note: firmware blobs are non-redistributable
      proprietary binaries shipped by the upstream repo.
